# JackLinx

Platform for the Music Classroom

[http://www.jacklinx.nl](http://www.jacklinx.nl)

## QUICK INSTALL ##

### Step 1 ###
Download repo as zip file from GitHUb

### Step 2 ###
Unzip the image into a directory with name ./jacklinx

### Step 3 ###
remove everything except:

- DEBIAN
- opt
- usr
- etc

### Step 4 ###
Bundle the image into a Debian Package by using command line:

dpkg ./jacklinx jacklinx.deb

### Step 5 ###
Use Gdebi to install the package jacklinx.deb
